![scoremap](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/39856231/133796345-21302c42-5102-4206-9352-0988a4a8d7af.png)

@AlexEMG How many iterations did you train? Could you give me an inside to your training parameters and which effnet you used? Maybe I can try to reproduce your correct results :P.
